  <section id="overview" class="tab-content active overview-hero">
    <h2>Our Seven Pillars of Integrity</h2>
    <p>As I aspire to serve as your Auditor, my advocacy is founded on a system that unites innovation and integrity. Through a digitally enhanced workflow, visual financial reporting, and transparent data-sharing practices, I aim to ensure every peso is traceable and accountable.My commitment lies in serving with professionalism, upholding confidentiality, and crafting a responsive platform that continuously evolves to meet our needs.</p>
  </section>

  <section id="platform" class="tab-content">
    <div class="card">
      <h2>Financial Transparency</h2>
      <p>Deliver monthly audit reports featuring detailed charts comparing budget vs. actual performance, cash-flow analyses, and trend graphs so every member sees exactly where funds go and can spot deviations easily.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h2>Digital Record-Keeping</h2>
      <p>Maintain a centralized, cloud-based repository for receipts and ledgers with standardized Excel templates—locked fields and dropdowns ensure consistency and automated reminders prompt timely uploads.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h2>Peer Financial Literacy</h2>
      <p>Host quarterly workshops on bookkeeping basics and advanced Excel auditing tools (pivot tables, macros), empowering every treasurer to maintain accurate records and share auditing responsibility.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h2>Proactive Issue Detection</h2>
      <p>Implement variance-analysis templates and pre-audit checklists to catch anomalies early, coupled with one-on-one pre-audit meetings to resolve discrepancies before they escalate.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h2>Continuous Improvement Feedback</h2>
      <p>Launch a dedicated suggestions channel and conduct monthly review meetings to evaluate process enhancements, pilot promising ideas, and integrate successful updates into our standard procedures.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h2>Ethical Stewardship</h2>
      <p>Ensure strict confidentiality for all financial data—reports remain unbiased and accessible only to authorized officers, cultivating trust and integrity throughout the organization.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h2>Data-Driven Decision Support</h2>
      <p>Develop a live dashboard displaying key metrics—pending submissions, upcoming deadlines, balances—and real-time insights to help the Executive Board make informed strategic decisions without delay.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

